    #content
      h1 Express Prefixr
      p Easily add vendored-properties to your CSS.

      .boxes
        .left
          p Insert your CSS here
          textarea#input
          .go-button
            button Prefix it!
        .right
          p And it will be prefixed and outputted here.
          textarea#output(readonly)
        .cf
      h2 Open API!
      p ExpressPrefixr has an open API. All you need to do is post
        code css=(value)
        | to
        code http://
          = host
          |/api/processor
      p The result will be your CSS with all prefixes. (:
      pre.code
        | ~ Â» curl http://localhost:3000/api/processor -d css='body { border-radius: 10px; }'
        | {
        |      "status": "success",
        |      "result": "body {\n  -webkit-border-radius: 10px;\n  -moz-border-radius: 10px;\n  -ms-border radius: 10px;\n  -o-border-radius: 10px;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n}"
        | }
